        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S) In nomine domini nostri Iehsu Chrisi eterni dei amen. Anno nativitate
                        eius millesimo centesimo nonagesimo secundo, sexto kalendas aprelis,
                        indictione decima. Ex huius instrumenti pateat recitatione quod nos
                            <persName>Albertinus</persName> quondam <persName>Molesti</persName> et
                            <persName>Oibertus</persName> germanus et quondam Molesti ambo simul pro
                        nobis et pro <persName>Franco</persName> germano nostro vendimus et tradimus
                        tibi <persName>Rolando</persName> confratri hospitalis Altepascensis,
                        recipienti pro domino <persName>Aldibrando</persName> rectore dicti <orgName
                            key="#Hospitals" ref="#juridical_persons/3206"><rs key="#Hospitals"
                                >hospitalis</rs>
                            <placeName key="#Hospitals" ref="#places/3207"
                            >Altepascensis</placeName></orgName>, unam nostram terre petiam que est
                        posita in plagis et finibus <placeName key="#Wine #Roads" ref="#places/3210"
                            >Putei</placeName> seu in loco ubi dicitur <rs key="#Wine">Vignale</rs>.
                        Que tenet unum caput in <rs key="#Roads">via publica</rs>, aliud in terra
                            <persName ref="#people/3217">Adimarii</persName> quondam <persName
                            ref="#people/3218">Alberti</persName> et <persName>Sardi</persName> eius
                        filii. Ambo latera tenet in terra dicti hospitalis Altepascensis. Que est
                        per mensuram stariora octo (…). <foreign>Prezzo</foreign>: mille sol.
                        bonorum denariorum pisani conii. <foreign>Pena</foreign>: in duplum. (…)
                        Actum apud <placeName ref="#places/63">Sanctam Mariam ad Montem</placeName>
                        et in <orgName key="#Churches"><rs key="#Churches">ecclesia</rs> Sancti
                            Dalmatii</orgName>. Preterea suprascruptus Albertinus et Oibertus
                        germani in pignore dederunt et tradiderunt dicto Rolando, recipienti pro
                        supradicto Aldibrando, rectore dicti hospitali, unam terre petiam positam in
                            <placeName ref="#places/284">Petriolo</placeName>. Que tenet unum caput
                        in terra <persName>Berlingarii</persName> plebani et
                            <persName>Ricce</persName> uxoris <persName>Rubacastelli</persName> et
                        quondam <persName>Corsi</persName>. Caput aliud tenet in terra ***, unum
                        laterum tenet in terra <persName>Uguicionis</persName> quondam
                            <persName>Guiducii</persName> et <persName>Ubaldi</persName> quondam
                            <persName>Bernardi</persName> et <persName>Bronaciani</persName> quondam
                            <persName>Dominici</persName>, aliud in terra dicti Uguicionis. Que est
                        stariora quatuor minus panori quatuor (…). <foreign>Pena</foreign>: dupli.
                        (…) <persName><name ref="Mainettus">Mainettus</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Bei">Bei</name></persName>,
                            <persName>Litoldus</persName> quondam <persName>Incalciati</persName>,
                            <persName>Ugolus</persName> quondam <persName>Serotini</persName>.
                        Suprascripti rogati <rs>testes</rs> interfuerunt. (S) Ego <persName
                            key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Leonardus">Leonardus</name></persName>
                        domni imperatoris <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> post traditam scripsi,
                        complevi et dedi.</ab>
